# Eusopht Website Revamp — Implementation Plan

## Overview

A full-site revamp of the Eusopht company website using **Next.js 16** (App Router) + **Tailwind CSS v4**.
The goal is a **premium, light-mode, software-agency site** that avoids the "vibe-coded" sameness problem by establishing a deliberate, distinctive design system **before** writing a single component.

**Reference inspiration**: [plavno.io](https://plavno.io) — specifically its floating navbar, generous whitespace, typographic hierarchy, color use, and structural clarity.

---

## Design System Decisions (settled)

### Color Palette
| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `--color-bg` | `#F8FAFB` | Page background (off-white, not pure white) |
| `--color-surface` | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, navbar, elevated surfaces |
| `--color-border` | `#E2E8F0` | Dividers, card borders |
| `--color-text-primary` | `#0F172A` | Headlines, dark body copy |
| `--color-text-secondary` | `#475569` | Subtitles, supporting copy |
| `--color-text-muted` | `#94A3B8` | Labels, captions, overlines |
| `--color-accent` | `#2563EB` | Electric blue — CTAs, links, highlights |
| `--color-accent-light` | `#EFF6FF` | Accent backgrounds, chip fills |
| `--color-accent-dark` | `#1D4ED8` | Hover states on accent |
| `--color-footer-bg` | `#F1F5F9` | Mid-tone light gray footer |

> [!NOTE]
> The accent blue (`#2563EB`) is deliberately a specific cobalt/electric blue — **not** the generic mid-blue of shadcn defaults. It's paired against off-white and navy text to feel polished rather than generic.

### Typography
| Role | Font | Weight | Size range |
|---|---|---|---|
| Display / Hero headlines | **Bricolage Grotesque** | 700–800 | 56px–80px |
| All other text | **Plus Jakarta Sans** | 400–700 | 14px–36px |
| Code / monospace | `ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular` | — | — |

**Typographic scale** (CSS custom properties):
- `--text-xs`: 12px / overlines, labels
- `--text-sm`: 14px / captions, meta
- `--text-base`: 16px / body copy
- `--text-lg`: 18px / lead paragraphs
- `--text-xl`: 20px / card titles
- `--text-2xl`: 24px → `--text-5xl`: 48px / section headings
- `--text-display`: 64px–80px / hero only (Bricolage Grotesque)

### Motion (Framer Motion)
- **Scroll-triggered fade-ins**: opacity 0→1, y: 24px→0, `duration: 0.5`, `ease: easeOut`
- **Hover lifts**: cards `translateY(-4px)`, `boxShadow` intensify
- **Stagger children**: service cards, stat counters stagger by `0.1s`
- **Page transitions**: simple fade via `AnimatePresence`
- **No**: particles, canvas animations, morphing shapes, parallax

### Icons
**Heroicons** (via `@heroicons/react`) — outline variant primary, solid for active/filled states.

