## Site Architecture

### Pages & Routes

| Route | Page | Priority |
|---|---|---|
| `/` | **Home** | Phase 1 |
| `/services` | Services overview | Phase 2 |
| `/services/[slug]` | Individual service pages | Phase 2 |
| `/work` | Portfolio / Work | Phase 3 |
| `/about` | About Us | Phase 3 |
| `/contact` | Contact (`mailto:` CTA only) | Phase 3 |

**No blog for this revamp.** Individual service slugs to include: `web-development`, `mobile-development`, `ai-automation`, `third-party-integrations`, `outsourcing`, `product-development`, `shopify`, `hubspot`, `zapier`, `ghl`, `stripe`, `playwright`.

### Navigation (Floating Pill Navbar)
- Fixed, `position: fixed`, `top: 20px`, `left/right: 24px` (Plavno-style)
- `border-radius: 24px`, white background, subtle box shadow
- Logo left | Nav links center | CTA button right
- Dropdown megamenu for "Services" on hover
- Mobile: hamburger with full-screen slide-down drawer

