## Component Architecture

### Shared / Layout
- `components/layout/Navbar.tsx` — Floating pill navbar with megamenu
- `components/layout/Footer.tsx` — Light gray footer with 4-column grid
- `components/layout/PageWrapper.tsx` — Framer Motion page transition wrapper

### UI Primitives (design system atoms)
- `components/ui/Button.tsx` — Primary, secondary, ghost variants
- `components/ui/Badge.tsx` — Overline labels / category tags
- `components/ui/Card.tsx` — Base card with hover lift animation
- `components/ui/SectionHeader.tsx` — Overline + headline + subtitle combo
- `components/ui/AnimatedSection.tsx` — Scroll-triggered fade-in wrapper

### Home Page Sections (in order)
1. `sections/home/HeroSection.tsx` — Headline, subtext, CTAs, stats bar, logo strip
2. `sections/home/ServicesGrid.tsx` — Card grid of key service offerings
3. `sections/home/WhyEusopht.tsx` — Differentiators / value propositions
4. `sections/home/ProcessSection.tsx` — How we work (numbered steps or timeline)
5. `sections/home/PortfolioPreview.tsx` — 3–4 featured work cards
6. `sections/home/Testimonials.tsx` — Client testimonials carousel
7. `sections/home/StatsSection.tsx` — Animated counters (projects, clients, years)
8. `sections/home/CTABanner.tsx` — Full-width CTA section before footer

