## Build Sequence

### Phase 1 — Design System + Home Page
1. `globals.css` — CSS custom properties, typography scale, reset
2. `app/layout.tsx` — Font loading, metadata, layout shell
3. UI primitives: Button, Badge, Card, SectionHeader, AnimatedSection
4. Navbar + Footer
5. All 8 Home page sections
6. Polish: responsive, accessibility, SEO meta

### Phase 2 — Services pages
7. Services overview page
8. Dynamic `[slug]` service page template
9. Content data file per service

### Phase 3 — Remaining pages
10. Portfolio / Work page
11. About page
12. Contact page

